data.description: Come see this charming 3 bed 2 bath home before its gone. This home located in the heart of Hampstead close to shopping, dining and nestled between two golf courses. Situated on a large lot that is almost half an acre you will find this spacious home in Hampstead. The home boasts a split floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, huge living room, a spacious dining room, a laundry room with utility sink and lots of storage, and a sun room that opens up to the very large deck. Once you step inside this inviting home you will notice the open and spacious feel that gives ample room for entertaining.  The kitchen boasts ample space and plenty of storage  and includes an island. Just behind the kitchen is a spacious dining area that has a sliding glass door that opens up to the large sun room with it's own A/C unit that overlooks the backyard that provides plenty of privacy. Do you just have to have that spa like feel? The master bath holds a surprise of its own, a very large soaking tub to relax. All the great features of this home don't stop there. This home also already has a transfer switch and is set up for a whole house generator. The back yard is beautifully landscaped with a workshop and greenhouse. Have a boat, trailer, camper, or RV, no problem here with plenty of space for parking. This home is move in ready.  We also can't forget to mention the close proximity to the beautiful Topsail beaches, boat ramps (public and private), golf courses, shopping, historic Wilmington, and all the other area attractions. The public boat ramp is just around the corner with all the ICWW has to offer, this home is in a prime area. The possibilities are almost endless. A unique find in the heart of Hampstead, take a look and make it your own before it's gone.. Are you still reading this? Act now before this property is SOLD
